snippet.title: MazyMazes Demo - English Ver.
snippet.description:
This is a demo of a DRPG app "MazyMazes English version" for Android.

elfspringfield official twitter
https://twitter.com/elfspringfield

Google Play URL
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.elfspringfield.chilledoutengine.min.mazymazes



The app contains materials made by the following creators.
[Backgrounds graphics]
Onso11
https://onso001.booth.pm/

[Monsters graphics]
Toriotto
https://www.pixiv.net/users/5887541

[Frame design]
Frame Design
https://frames-design.com/

[BGM]
PeriTune
https://peritune.com/

[SEs]
Komori Taira
https://taira-komori.jpn.org/index.html
